    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ CUM DEUS OMNIPOTENS PER INFINITAM MAIESTATIS SUE CLEMENCIAM MULTIMODAS
                        RERUM VARIETATES FECISSET ET HOMINEM PRO VITE CELESTIS RESTAURACIONE
                        CONDIDISSET ET ILLE DIABOLICO SUASU A CONDITORIS SUI MANDATIS IN PECCATUM
                        DECIDISSET PATERNA PROVIDENCIA FILIUM SUUM AD PRIMI TERRIGENE PECCATUM
                        ABOLENDUM IN TERRAM MISIT; QUI POST SUAM PASSIONEM ET AD CELUM REMEACIONEM
                        PRO HUMANORUM CORPORUM MUNICIONE ET ANIMARUM REDEPTIONE ECCLESIAM SIBI IN
                        TERRA CONSTRUI JUSSIT; CUI QUIA NOS IPSO MONENTE TRIBUTUM PERSOLVERE JUBEMUR
                        EGO <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3001">RICARDUS</persName> DEI
                        GRACIA CAPUANUS <rs key="#Princeps">PRINCEPS</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3000">SANCTI PETRI AC
                            SANCTI LAURETII</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">CENOBIO</rs> IN TERCIA PARTE <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/4000">ADVERSI</placeName> MILIARII SITO ATQUE <rs
                            key="#Abbots">ABBATI</rs>
                        <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3046">RADULFO</persName> SUISQUE
                        SUCCESSORIBUS DO ET CONCEDO <rs key="#Decima">DECIMAM</rs> PORCIONIS MEE
                        QUAM TENEO SUPER <rs key="#Rivers">FLUMEN</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/609" key="#Rivers #Decima">VULTURNUM</placeName>; IN
                            <rs key="#Castle">CASTELLO</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Document_features #Castle #Decima" ref="#places/4059"
                            >SCLAVIUM</placeName>; IN <placeName ref="#places/4052"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Decima">ARNONE</placeName>; IN <placeName
                            ref="#places/4060" key="#Villages/settlements #Decima"
                            >ROSELLO</placeName>; IN <placeName ref="#places/4061"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Decima">ODORICIS</placeName>; USQUE AD
                            <placeName key="#Fortress #Decima" ref="#places/4062">CASTELLUM
                            MARIS;</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Decima">DECIMAM</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cereals">ANNONE</rs> TERRE QUE MICHI ACCIDIT. ET <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wine">VINI</rs> ARBORUM; ET EA DICTIONE. HOC
                        DO ET CONCEDO. UT SI QUIS CALUMPNIARE PRESUMPSERIT; PRIMUM IRAM DEI
                        INCURRAT. ET QUOD PECIERIT NON ADQUIRAT. ET UT HEC KARTULA FIRMIOR SIT;
                        PROPRIA MANU EGO EAM FIRMAVI + FACTA EST HEC DONACIO KALENDAS MAJ. IN ILLO
                        ANNO QUO OBIIT <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/3047"
                            >KENRICUS</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">REX</rs> GALLIE <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #childOf" ref="#people/3048">PHILIPO</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">FILIO</rs> EJUS <rs key="#Emperor/king">IN REGNO ILLI
                            SUCCEDENTE</rs>. ATQUE <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1974"
                            >NICOLAO</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">PAPA</rs> ROMANE ECCLESIE PRESIDENTE; RICHARDUS PRINCEPS
                        +</ab>
